<div class="w-full">
  <div class="sm:flex sm:items-center">
    <div class="sm:flex-auto">
      <h1 class="text-base font-semibold leading-6 text-gray-900">Feature Flags & Configuration</h1>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-700">Current values of probability calculation configuration and feature flags.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="mt-8 flow-root">
    <div class="-mx-4 -my-2 sm:-mx-6 lg:-mx-8">
      <div class="inline-block min-w-full py-2 align-middle sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="overflow-hidden shadow ring-1 ring-black ring-opacity-5 sm:rounded-lg">
          <table class="min-w-full divide-y divide-gray-300">
            <thead class="bg-gray-50">
              <tr>
                <th scope="col" class="py-3.5 pl-4 pr-3 text-left text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 sm:pl-6">Setting</th>
                <th scope="col" class="px-3 py-3.5 text-left text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900">Value</th>
                <th scope="col" class="px-3 py-3.5 text-left text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900">Description</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-200 bg-white">
              <tr>
                <td class="whitespace-nowrap py-4 pl-4 pr-3 text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 sm:pl-6">
                  <code class="text-xs bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded">use_ema_calculation</code>
                </td>
                <td class="whitespace-nowrap px-3 py-4 text-sm text-gray-500">
                  <% if @config.use_ema_calculation %>
                    <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-md bg-green-50 px-2 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-green-700 ring-1 ring-inset ring-green-600/20">Enabled</span>
                  <% else %>
                    <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-md bg-gray-50 px-2 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-gray-700 ring-1 ring-inset ring-gray-600/20">Disabled</span>
                  <% end %>
                  <div class="mt-1 text-xs text-gray-400">
                    ENV: <code><%= ENV['USE_EMA_PROBABILITY'] || 'not set (default: false)' %></code>
                  </div>
                </td>
                <td class="px-3 py-4 text-sm text-gray-500">
                  When enabled, uses the new EMA-based probability calculation. When disabled, uses the legacy calculation method.
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="whitespace-nowrap py-4 pl-4 pr-3 text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 sm:pl-6">
                  <code class="text-xs bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded">lambda</code>
                </td>
                <td class="whitespace-nowrap px-3 py-4 text-sm text-gray-500">
                  <code class="text-sm"><%= number_with_precision(@config.lambda, precision: 4) %></code>
                  <div class="mt-1 text-xs text-gray-400">
                    ENV: <code><%= ENV['PROBABILITY_LAMBDA'] || 'not set (default: 0.15)' %></code>
                  </div>
                </td>
                <td class="px-3 py-4 text-sm text-gray-500">
                  Exponential Moving Average decay factor. Higher values = more responsive to recent results, less weight on history. Default: 0.15 (15%).
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="whitespace-nowrap py-4 pl-4 pr-3 text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 sm:pl-6">
                  <code class="text-xs bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded">combiner_home_weight</code>
                </td>
                <td class="whitespace-nowrap px-3 py-4 text-sm text-gray-500">
                  <code class="text-sm"><%= number_with_precision(@config.combiner_home_weight, precision: 4) %></code>
                  <div class="mt-1 text-xs text-gray-400">
                    ENV: <code><%= ENV['PROBABILITY_COMBINER_HOME_WEIGHT'] || 'not set (default: 0.6)' %></code>
                  </div>
                </td>
                <td class="px-3 py-4 text-sm text-gray-500">
                  Weight for home team's home probability when combining with away team's away probability. Default: 0.6 (60%).
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="whitespace-nowrap py-4 pl-4 pr-3 text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 sm:pl-6">
                  <code class="text-xs bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded">combiner_away_weight</code>
                </td>
                <td class="whitespace-nowrap px-3 py-4 text-sm text-gray-500">
                  <code class="text-sm"><%= number_with_precision(@config.combiner_away_weight, precision: 4) %></code>
                  <div class="mt-1 text-xs text-gray-400">
                    Calculated: <code>1 - home_weight</code>
                  </div>
                </td>
                <td class="px-3 py-4 text-sm text-gray-500">
                  Weight for away team's away probability when combining. Automatically calculated to ensure weights sum to 1.0.
                </td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-6 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-4">
          <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 mb-3">Raw Configuration Values</h3>
          <div class="bg-white rounded border border-gray-300 p-4 overflow-x-auto">
            <pre class="text-xs text-gray-800 font-mono"><code>config.probability = {
<% @config.each do |key, value| -%>
  <%= key %>: <%= value.inspect %>,
<% end -%>
}</code></pre>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-3 text-xs text-gray-600">
            <p>All properties of <code>Rails.application.config.probability</code>:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-1 space-y-1">
              <% @config.each do |key, value| -%>
                <li><code><%= key %></code>: <%= value.class.name %> = <%= value.inspect %></li>
              <% end -%>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-6 bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-4">
          <div class="flex">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-400" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M18 10a8 8 0 11-16 0 8 8 0 0116 0zm-7-4a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zM9 9a.75.75 0 000 1.5h.253a.25.25 0 01.244.304l-.459 2.066A1.75 1.75 0 0010.747 15H11a.75.75 0 000-1.5h-.253a.25.25 0 01-.244-.304l.459-2.066A1.75 1.75 0 009.253 9H9z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="ml-3">
              <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-blue-800">How to Change Values</h3>
              <div class="mt-2 text-sm text-blue-700">
                <p>These values are controlled by environment variables. To change them:</p>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 space-y-1">
                  <li><code class="bg-blue-100 px-1 rounded">USE_EMA_PROBABILITY=true</code> - Enable EMA calculation</li>
                  <li><code class="bg-blue-100 px-1 rounded">PROBABILITY_LAMBDA=0.15</code> - Set EMA decay factor</li>
                  <li><code class="bg-blue-100 px-1 rounded">PROBABILITY_COMBINER_HOME_WEIGHT=0.6</code> - Set home team weight</li>
                </ul>
                <p class="mt-2">After changing environment variables, restart the application server.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
